GSD.description:
net: dsa: tag_8021q: avoid leaking ctx on dsa_tag_8021q_register() error path

This is an automated ID intended to aid in discovery of potential security vulnerabilities. The actual impact and attack plausibility have not yet been proven.
This ID is fixed in Linux Kernel version v5.15.86 by commit 09f30f394e832ed09859b6a80fdd20668a9104ff, it was introduced in version v5.15 by commit 328621f6131f667c5c328bb72d45442fd76efb81. For more details please see the references link.
